#551
On the Island~
As you pull yourself up from the river, you find yourself on a fascinating
island.  Trees and rocks line the shore and watch the river lazily meander by.
Ahead in the distance you see a mist shrouded mountain, which seems strangely
large for such a dainty island.  Perhaps there is magic in the air.
