#552
A Quiet Glade~
You are in the midst of a quiet, moonlit glade.  The trees line the shore
of the river and shield this glade from outsiders.  To the northeast you can
see the huge mountain rising out of the mists, appearing as a giant guardiang
of peace in this tranquil setting.  Beneath a large willow, a large blanket
has been set out.  A basket sits beside it, as well as a bucket containing a
bottle of champagne.  A gilded candleabra sheds a warm glow over the blanket,
making you feel very relaxed and comfortable.
