#5593
Boudouir~
You step inside a large, comfortable bedroom. You are immediately welcomed by
the scent of sweet smelling herbs and incense. Against the far wall a huge
canopy bed with carved wooden posts and white gauze drapes beckons you to lay
your body down on it's soft, purple velvet bedspread. A fireplace sets against
the opposite wall, crackling softly and warming your skin. Standing in the
center of the room is a shiny black upright piano resonating softly in your ear
with each beautiful note. In the corner stands a divine statue of the goddess
Venus, her long beautiful hair flowing and curling down her naked body. All
around her are beautiful, exotic flowers that you have never seen before. In
front of her steam arises in gentle clouds, scented with freshly picked rose
petals from the hot tub. On the wall behind the bed you notice a few strange
looking hooks attatched with long strips of black silk...
~
